## ğŸ¯ Next Steps (5 minutes to deploy)

### 1. Create GitHub Repository
```bash
# Create new repo on GitHub called "gifbeat-waitlist"
# Upload all files from gifbeat-waitlist folder
```

### 2. Set Up Supabase (Free)
1. Go to [supabase.com](https://supabase.com) â†’ Create Project
2. Copy your Project URL and Anon Key
3. Run this SQL in Supabase SQL Editor:

```sql
CREATE TABLE waitlist (
  id UUID DEFAULT gen_random_uuid() PRIMARY KEY,
  email TEXT UNIQUE NOT NULL,
  created_at TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE DEFAULT NOW()
);

CREATE POLICY "Anyone can insert email" ON waitlist FOR INSERT WITH CHECK (true);
ALTER TABLE waitlist ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;
```

### 3. Deploy to Vercel (Free)
1. Go to [vercel.com](https://vercel.com) â†’ Import GitHub repo
2. Add environment variables:
   - `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL` = your Supabase URL
   - `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` = your Supabase anon key
3. Click Deploy â†’ Done! ğŸ‰

